Alstom, EADS Will Invest in Vekselberg Project, Echos Reports

-- B y   G r e g o r y   V i s c u s i
-- 
2011-03-03T06:59:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-03/alstom-eads-will-invest-in-vekselberg-project-echos-reports.html
  Alstom SA (ALO)  and European Aeronautic,
Defence & Space Co. will invest in a Russian “Silicon Valley”
being developed west of Moscow,  Les Echos  reported, citing an
interview with  Viktor Vekselberg , a Russian financier heading
the project.  EADS will concentrate on communication projects, and Alstom
on clean energy, Vekselberg said, according to the newspaper. He
controls holding company Renova Group.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Gregory Viscusi in Paris at 
 gviscusi@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editors responsible for this story:
James Hertling at 
 jhertling@bloomberg.net . 